One-time minister Julius Sunkuli has sent a message of condolence to the family, friends and relatives of former Nyeri Governor Wahome Gakuru. He described Gakuru’s death as a big loss, not only to Nyeri residents, but all Kenyans. Sunkuli spoke to journalists in Kericho town after filing a petition challenging the election of Colonel (Rtd) Gideon Konchela as the Kilgoris MP.              